    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older car in fair, honest condition and priced accordingly. It is complete and usable as-is, but it shows clear age-related wear inside and out, with visible cosmetic imperfections, a driver-quality presentation, and the kind of flaws you would expect from an older car that has been used and enjoyed rather than fully restored. A good fit for someone looking for an affordable entry point into ownership and willing to accept some imperfections and ongoing sorting.",
