    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "Runs and drives well. This is a good-condition car with a solid overall appearance, normal wear inside and out, and no major cosmetic issues beyond typical age and use. It appears to have been reasonably maintained, but like any used vehicle, expect routine upkeep.",
