    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Mint-condition example that stands out for its exceptionally clean presentation, careful ownership, and premium overall feel. This is the kind of vehicle that inspires confidence the moment you see it\u2014beautifully maintained, sharp inside and out, and ready to impress its next owner. A rare opportunity to own a truly top-tier used vehicle at an excellent value.",
