    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Absolutely gorgeous car that\u2019s been lovingly cared for and it shows. Super clean inside and out, runs beautifully, and has that hard-to-find feel of a vehicle that\u2019s truly been kept right. If you\u2019re after something sharp, dependable, and ready to enjoy from day one, this one will make a great impression. Priced to reflect the condition and value here, but still a very fair buy for the right person.",
      "price": 46900.0,
