      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offered in truly mint condition, this car is exceptionally clean inside and out and presents like a meticulously kept enthusiast-owned example. The powertrain pulls strong, shifts are crisp, and the chassis feels tight and composed with no odd noises or drama\u2014exactly how a properly maintained car should. Paint has a deep gloss, the cabin is fresh and well-preserved, and everything reflects careful ownership and regular upkeep. If you want a sharp, turn-key car that looks right, drives right, and stands out from the average used example, this one is absolutely worth a close look.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
